Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:38.27,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}籠の中は安全で　绝对なのだと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.31,0:04:43.40,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}創造すら忘れた　その座に光は当たんないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:45.87,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}希望語る　不満散らす
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.87,0:04:47.76,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}革命の合図
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:51.28,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}誰にも追いつけないところまで
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.32,0:04:58.31,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}突き抜け　修羅を越え　いつか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:05:03.79,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}今にも圧倒的な支配が　僕の喉を乾かしたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.87,0:05:08.39,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}奪わせないものは夢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.54,0:05:11.24,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}燃やせ　全神経の感覚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:15.98,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}誰に届けたいかすらもわからない音に
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:21.16,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}意義は宿らない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.91,0:05:26.68,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}光を　もっと光を
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:30.72,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}その頂へと
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,//------------------OPCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:38.27,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}牢笼里多么的安全　舒适而没有压力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.31,0:04:43.40,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}忘却了创造　这里将被光明抛弃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:45.87,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}来倾吐希望　让不满爆发
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.87,0:04:47.76,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}吹响革新的号角
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:51.28,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我要全力攀登　再不让他人企及
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.32,0:04:58.31,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}突破血雨腥风　让他们全都辟易
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:05:03.79,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}绝对的控制　将令我咽喉干渴无法言语
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.87,0:05:08.39,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}却无法夺去我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.54,0:05:11.24,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}让一切感官嘶吼激昂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:15.98,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}不把炽热的情感寄托在音符中唱响
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:21.16,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}怎会令心脏热血滚烫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.91,0:05:26.68,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我需要光　更多的光
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:30.72,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}向着顶点冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:33.28,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Have an obsession for victory
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:35.90,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I'm proud of myself and you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.96,0:05:38.78,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}We must be the change we wish to see
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,//------------------EDJP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.65,0:22:21.84,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}青天響く霹靂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.10,0:22:25.20,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}閃光眩むその間に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.71,0:22:32.38,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}決して音を立てずに　じっと忍び寄る影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.55,0:22:35.97,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}騙し騙されて 失った
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.07,0:22:39.42,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}罵り罵られて 奪った
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.61,0:22:43.45,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}守りべき正義をすり減らして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.57,0:22:46.81,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}勝ち取るものなどない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.90,0:22:50.48,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}籠の中から見上げた空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.64,0:22:54.05,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}雨上がりの青の眩しさに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.21,0:22:57.48,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}囚われたままじゃ居られない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.48,0:23:00.97,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}昔話なら捨てて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.97,0:23:04.53,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}従うべきは他でもない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.71,0:23:08.20,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}突き動かすほどの本能だ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:11.60,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}ぼくはぼくじゃなきゃ居られない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.60,0:23:14.82,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}変われるほど器用じゃないさ
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,//------------------EDCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.65,0:22:21.84,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}响彻青天的霹雳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.10,0:22:25.20,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}闪光掠过的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.71,0:22:32.38,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}无声无息　阴影迫近
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.55,0:22:35.97,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}尔虞我诈　逐渐失去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.07,0:22:39.42,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}以眼还眼　互相争夺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.61,0:22:43.45,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}逐渐磨损本该保护的正以
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.57,0:22:46.81,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}也绝对不会赢得任何东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.90,0:22:50.48,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}在笼中仰望到的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.64,0:22:54.05,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}雨过天晴眩目的蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.21,0:22:57.48,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}不甘永远被囚禁于此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.48,0:23:00.97,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}哪怕要让我舍弃过去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.97,0:23:04.53,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}要遵从之物仅有一件
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.71,0:23:08.20,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}本能激发着无穷动力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:11.60,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}无论如何都要做自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.60,0:23:14.82,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}因为改变对我是难题
